data.description: Charming Cape Cod-style home in Clifton, NJ, boasting three bedrooms and one bathroom. This cozy residence features classic architecture with a welcoming front facade and great curb appeal. Inside, you'll find a functional layout with ample living space including first floor bedroom and full bath and perfect for anyone seeking comfort and convenience. The home offers a cozy living room, a well-appointed kitchen and a formal dining room which opens to your outdoor oasis. 2nd floor features two comfortably sized bedrooms. This property completes with a full finished basement that is the perfect recitational area and additional living space. With its convenient location in Clifton, residents enjoy easy access to local amenities, schools and transportation options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this delightful Cape Cod home sweet home. Requesting Highest & Best offers
